description: We keep an eye on the world's professional job market, giving you everything you need to instantly profile people, jobs and skills. The Skill Report API offers detailed skills data to improve financial risk modelling, marketing segmentation, human resource analytics, lead scoring, content personalization and recruitment. If you need to make connections between skills and the value of jobs and people, then the Skill Report API will help you get started immediately. You can see some of our API data in action at http://skill.report.
